fields.alternativename: alternative name of field -- this is the one usually shown to users

annotation.annotationflags: annotation flags from /F -- see pdf_annotation_flag_e in qpdf/Constants.h
annotation.appearancestate: appearance state -- can be used to determine value for checkboxes and radio buttons

fields.choices: for choices fields, the list of choices presented to the user
fields.fieldflags: form field flags from /Ff -- see pdf_form_field_flag_e in qpdf/Constants.h
fields.ischoice: whether field is a list, combo, or dropdown
fields.isradiobutton: whether field is a radio button -- buttons in a single group share a parent
fields.istext: whether field is a text field
fields.pageposfrom1: position of containing page numbered from 1
fields.quadding: field quadding -- number indicating left, center, or right

acroform.hasacroform: whether the document has interactive forms
acroform.needappearances: whether the form fields' appearance streams need to be regenerated

encrypt.ownerpasswordmatched: whether supplied password matched owner password; always false for non-encrypted files

parameters.key: encryption key; will be null unless --show-encryption-key was specified
parameters.method: overall encryption method: none, mixed, RC4, AESv2, AESv3

encrypt.userpasswordmatched: whether supplied password matched user password; always false for non-encrypted files

stream.filter: if stream, its filters, otherwise null
stream.is: whether the object is a stream
stream.length: if stream, its length, otherwise null

objects: dictionary of original objects; keys are 'trailer' or 'n n R'

outlines.destpageposfrom1: position of destination page in document numbered from 1; null if not known
outlines.open: whether the outline is displayed expanded
outlines.title: outline title

pagelabels.index: starting page position starting from zero
pagelabels.label: page label dictionary

images.filterable: whether image data can be decoded using the decode level qpdf was invoked with
images.name: name of image in XObject table

pages.label: page label dictionary, or null if none

outlines.object: reference to outline that targets this page
outlines.title: outline title

pages.pageposfrom1: position of page in document numbering from 1

parameters.decodelevel: decode level used to determine stream filterability

version: JSON format serial number; increased for non-compatible changes
